Edited web/src/components/metrics/metrics-content.css (2 lines -> 1 lines)### Group 5: Fix LabelColor type - `cyan` and `gold` are not valid in PF6

In PF6, `Label` color prop accepts: `"blue" | "green" | "grey" | "orange" | "orangered" | "purple" | "red" | "teal" | "yellow"`. The old `cyan` → `teal` and `gold` → `yellow`.
